lt_eq_not_ge:
theorem lt_eq_not_ge [LT α] [decidable_rel ((· < ·) : α → α → Prop)] : ∀ l₁ l₂ : list α, (l₁ < l₂) = ¬l₂ ≤ l₁ :=
  fun l₁ l₂ => show (l₁ < l₂) = ¬¬l₁ < l₂ from eq.subst (propext (not_not_iff (l₁ < l₂))).symm rfl
#align lt_eq_not_ge lt_eq_not_ge
le_eq_not_gt:

theorem le_eq_not_gt [LT α] : ∀ l₁ l₂ : list α, (l₁ ≤ l₂) = ¬l₂ < l₁ := fun l₁ l₂ => rfl
#align le_eq_not_gt le_eq_not_gt
